{"name":"Moser Woormwool","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"any race","alignment":"any alignment","hitDice":"10","armorName":"chain mail","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (splint)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"65 (10d8 + 20)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"16","dexPoints":"13","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"10","wisPoints":"13","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"4","customCr":"3 (700 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The veteran can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The veteran regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the veteran can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the veteran can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The veteran can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the veteran's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the veteran's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the veteran dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[],"actions":[{"name":"Raise the Alarm!","desc":"[MON] takes the dodge action and blows a horn, raising the alarm:\n\nRoll 1d6 on initiative count 20:\n1-4: 1d4 Harport Goons arrive\n5: 1 Harport Goon and 1 Harport Thug arrive\n6: Harps Walks-on-Water arrives (with 2 goons), and immediately gets a turn"},{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] two mace attacks. If it has a shortsword drawn, it can also make a shortsword attack as a bonus action."},{"name":"Mace","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D8] bludgeoning damage."},{"name":"Shortsword","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1d6] piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Shortsword","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [1d6] piercing damage."}],"reactions":[{"name":"You Do It!","desc":"If one of [MON]'s allies misses an attack or fails an ability check within 30 ft, [MON] can use his reaction to command another ally within 30ft to move their speed, swap places with another ally, and make an attack."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"any one language (usually Common)","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Moser","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}